      "text": "A complex mixture of polypeptide components. Neurotoxicity is the most clinically relevant.\nHistamine and other components potentiate localized swelling and vascular permeability\nSeveral neurotoxic components that activate sodium channels, potentiating action potentials and causing uncontrolled muscle contractions.",
