    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Initial intense pain that radiates to the trunk\nWithin 10-20 minutes, onset of systemic toxicity\nTachycardia\nHypertension\nProfuse diaphoresis,\nSalivation\nVertigo\nVisual disturbances\nNausea and vomiting\nPriapism\nDeath has been reported, particularly in children and frail adults, from respiratory paralysis\nMost recover in 24-48hours",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
